WEBVTT

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:08.000
Question, what would you say is one of the greatest gifts that we received from Jehovah?

00:00:09.439 --> 00:00:15.039
Interestingly, the comment that we'll read in a few minutes from the White Star says that perhaps

00:00:15.599 --> 00:00:21.199
one of the greatest gifts that we receive from Jehovah is our ability to worship him.

00:00:22.239 --> 00:00:26.800
And this gift goes hand in hand with another gift that Jehovah has given us which is highlighted

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:35.119
in today's text. That is our ability to love. But when you think of an ability, an ability is only

00:00:35.119 --> 00:00:42.719
of value if it is developed and if it is put to good use. For example, the child is born with the

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:51.840
ability to walk, but that ability will be of no value if it's not developed and not put to use.

00:00:52.479 --> 00:00:58.799
So use our question then, how can we continue to develop our ability to love?

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:07.359
Let's consider two steps. Step number one, by imitating our loving father, Jehovah.

00:01:07.359 --> 00:01:14.799
