00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:28.159
appreciates that we're trying to be like him. That takes us to our second step where we find it

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:34.879
in verse two. Paul says to go on walking in love. So that's our second step. Walking in love

00:03:35.439 --> 00:03:42.879
just as the Christ also loved us and gave himself for us as an offering and a sacrifice

